race.comment: Race drops right away outside the top few chances. Hard to go past STROMBOLI DELIGHT (7) who is knocking on the door, the latest a fast finishing second at Gatton. Back up to a mile again and looks ideal now. Gets chance. ATTACK FORCE (1) has also been racing over shorter journeys. On the quick back up a week after finishing fourth here over 1200m. Can improve sharply this extra trip. STYLISH ANGEL (8) is fitter for three runs in and looks suited to the mile now. Should prove hard to beat with the claim. STRIKE ME PINK (9) is better than last start and can sneak into the finish with the right run. OHH ERROL (12) finds a suitable race and can give a sight off the low draw.
